text: Nordre Ål Church is from 1994 in Lillehammer Municipality, Innlandet County. The structure is made of concrete and wood and has a capacity of 600 seats. ==Nordre Ål Parish== Gårdsnummer 37-58 were included in this parishLillehammer annekssogn.
